title: Looking for a duo and people to play flex with - Gold 4
body:
Looking a duo to play and climb with GOLD+ preferred. Also looking for a Flex crew to run with rank doesn't matter too much in that. I play most nights normally 8-9pm onwards but can be on earlier
MY tag is II DeCeiVeD II (ii deceived ii) Ranks are gold 4 in solo/duo and silver 5 in flex(haven't played much flex) add me in game if interested
